  "texts": [
    "A critical aspect of the MultiSenseBadminton dataset is its public availability.",
    "As such, explicit consent was also obtained for the public release of data that includes personally identifiable information (PII), specifically the video recordings of participants performing badminton swing.",
    "The videos have undergone mosaic or blur processing for participant confidentiality.",
    "The final MultiSenseBadminton dataset comprises video, annotation, personal information and sensor data from all 25 participants who participated in the study, each of whom consented to the release of their personal data for public access.",
    "Participants."
